summary: (NOT A REMAKE, ACTUAL FACE.) This mod adds a new preset with the original Farengar npc head to the list of Nord presets, allowing you to pick and edit it all you want.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a new preset with the original Farengar npc head to the list of Nord presets, allowing you to pick and edit it all you want.

You can use it and share it or w/e, yadayadayada, as long as you credit me for spending those long 2 minutes to make this mod.
author: sirwolfington
